ag-blessing-al-barakah","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-manners-adab","tag-marriage-al-nikah","tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-virtue-al-fadail"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8gp","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":14191,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/05\/13\/righteous-wives-dutiful\/","url_meta":{"origin":31769,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: Obedience to husband in marital duties","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: It was said to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, \u201cWhich wives are best?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cOne who pleases him when he looks at her, obeys him when he requests her, and does not oppose him in regards to intimacy with herself\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11826,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/25\/nikah-marry-righteous-fasad\/","url_meta":{"origin":31769,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Marriage: Marry the righteous or else there is corruption","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf someone proposes marriage to you whose religion and character satisfies you, then you should accept it. If you do not do so, there will be trials on the earth and the spread of corruption.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/10\/ghirah-allah-loves-and-hates\/","url_meta":{"origin":31769,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Gheerah: Protective jealousy that Allah loves and hates","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAmong protective jealousy is what Allah loves and hates. As for what Allah loves, it is jealousy when there is probable cause. As for what Allah hates, it is jealousy without probable cause.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3735,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/07\/20\/supplication-iftar\/","url_meta":{"origin":31769,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Fasting: The Prophet\u2019s supplication upon breaking his fast","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported:\u00a0The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would say\u00a0upon breaking the fast, \u201cGone is the thirst, quenched are the veins, and assured is the reward if Allah wills.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 2357 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0646 \u0639\u0645\u0631 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0643\u064e\u0627\u0646\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064